      <title></title>
      <link href="/2024/08/02/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Scoop%E7%9A%84%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B%E4%B8%80%E7%AF%87/"/>
      <url>/2024/08/02/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Scoop%E7%9A%84%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B%E4%B8%80%E7%AF%87/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="安装使用Scoop的教程一篇"><a href="#安装使用Scoop的教程一篇" class="headerlink" title="安装使用Scoop的教程一篇"></a>安装使用Scoop的教程一篇</h1><blockquote><p>作业来的</p></blockquote><p><a href="chatgpt.com" title="善用互联网">什么是scoop</a></p><h2 id="安装的主要流程"><a href="#安装的主要流程" class="headerlink" title="安装的主要流程"></a>安装的主要流程</h2><p>1.&#x3D;&#x3D;更改组策略设置!&#x3D;&#x3D;<a href="%E5%9C%A8**Windows%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE**%E4%B8%AD%E6%9F%A5%E6%89%BE**%E7%BC%96%E8%BE%91%E7%BB%84%E7%AD%96%E7%95%A5**%EF%BC%8C%E4%BE%9D%E5%BA%8F%E6%89%93%E5%BC%80**Windows%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE**%EF%BC%8C**%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE**%EF%BC%8C**%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E7%AD%96%E7%95%A5**%EF%BC%8C**%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E9%80%89%E9%A1%B9**%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E5%8F%B3%E4%BE%A7%E5%90%AF%E7%94%A8**%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8E%E5%86%85%E7%BD%AE%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%91%98%E8%B4%A6%E6%88%B7%E7%9A%84%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%91%98%E6%89%B9%E5%87%86%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F**%EF%BC%8C%E4%B9%8B%E5%90%8E==%E9%87%8D%E5%90%AF==">^方法</a>否则会无法运行<br>2.使用<strong>win+R</strong>输入<strong>powershell</strong>，运行<strong>iwr -useb get.scoop.sh | iex</strong><br>3.如果出现<strong>Scoop was installed successfully</strong>，那么安装成功</p><h2 id="更改下载源的方式"><a href="#更改下载源的方式" class="headerlink" title="更改下载源的方式"></a>更改下载源的方式</h2><blockquote><p>原下载源在境外，下载麻烦</p></blockquote><ol><li>打开powershell或cmd</li><li>更换scoop的repo地址 <figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">scoop config SCOOP_REPO <span class="string">&quot;https://gitee.com/scoop-installer/scoop&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>拉取新库地址<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">scoop update</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h2 id="scoop的简单应用"><a href="#scoop的简单应用" class="headerlink" title="scoop的简单应用"></a>scoop的简单应用</h2><ul><li>安装（以<strong>everything</strong>[^1]为例）<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">scoop install everything</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img src="/" alt="安装"></li><li>卸载（以<strong>everything</strong>[^1]为例）<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">scoop uninstall everything</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img src="C:\Users\Administrator\Desktop\QQ截图20240730203612.png" alt="卸载"></li><li>查找可用软件<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">scoop search</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><p><img src="C:\Users\Administrator\Desktop\QQ截图20240730203006.png" alt="如图"><br>[^1]:检索工具</p><p><img src="https://p0.ssl.qhimgs1.com/t0492ef05fc73f819d4.jpg" alt="蛋糕"></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
